snippet.title: Ivan Miranda
snippet.description: I make projects about what makes me tick. I'm into digital fabrication, 3D printing, electronics, woodworking, instrument making, metalworking, and anything geeky in general. I'll try to give as much info as possible about my projects so anyone can try an replicate. Hope you like my projects, don't forget to subscribe to be updated about my new contraptions!
